        <h2>Getting Started with Mega City Cab</h2>
        <p>Follow the steps below to get started:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Login:</strong> Use your username and password to login to the system.</li>
            <li><strong>Manage Cars:</strong> Add, update, or remove cars from the fleet.</li>
            <li><strong>Manage Drivers:</strong> Add, update, or remove drivers from the system.</li>
            <li><strong>Create Booking:</strong> Customers can book a ride by selecting a car and entering their details.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Common Issues</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>If you forget your password, please contact support.</li>
            <li>Ensure your internet connection is stable when booking a ride.</li>
